== Introduction ==

This page has been created to report the Release Party Held in Rome on June 9.

The publication of this event was given as follows:
* [http://fedoraproject.org/wiki/Fedora_17_Release_Party section "Events" of the Fedora Project wiki]
* [http://www.fedoraonline.it/content/pizzata-fedora-e-release-party-f17 Italian Community of it.fedoracommunity.org]
* [http://lists.fedoraproject.org/pipermail/ambassadors/2012-June/019752.html Ambassadors Mailing List]
* [http://www.lffl.org/2012/06/fedora-release-pizza-party-roma-sabato.html www.lffl.com]

The initiative was for the users who wanted take a look to the community and to the new release '''' 'Fedora'' 17''' '''' '' Beefy Miracle'' '"'' .

The chosen location was Rome for many reasons, including:
* Is the capital of Italy;
* Is the center of our country;
* Is accessible by all means of transport;
* It is a historical and artistic city.

The italian Ambassador also wanted  to check the interest of users in different contexts.

