== Participants ==

The event was attended by 16 people including who were approaching the Fedora world, and with we had an interesting exchange of views.

These users have been particularly required to take a look at the operations with Gnome3 and an overview of the system.

Presentations == ==

[[File: Giallu1.jpg | 370px | left | Giallu]] [[File: gabri.jpg | 370px | right | mailga]] Gianluca Sforna proceeded to explain the new release, with particular reference to features and improvements occurring in the system, with practical examples, including the terminal use and the Gnome 3 functionality. <br/>

Gabriele Trombini explaining the present activities of the Project, the concept of free software, and the relationship between Fedora Project and Contributors.
<br/>
<br/>
